<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="more-and-more">more and more</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-increasingly">1.<strong>越来越 (多的 / 地) (increasingly)</strong></h4>
<p>反 less and less </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>More and more people are using smart phones for information and entertainment.
越来越多的人在用智能手机获取信息和娱乐。</p></div></div>